data.description: Beautifully remodeled 3 bedroom, 1.75 bath rambler on large fully fenced corner lot. This home is filled with natural light, lives large and has AC! Open floor plan features a living room w/ fireplace, kitchen w/stainless appliances, plenty of storage, white shaker cabinets, quartz counter tops, designer backsplash and oversized peninsula! Walk through the dining room and step down to family room w/ built-in cabinets. Large primary suite features 3/4 ensuite bath, 2 additional bedrooms w/ walk-in closets. Outdoor space is perfect for entertaining, and even has a 7 zone sprinkler system! Two car garage and RV parking! Outbuilding/shed has power and could be a great work space, workout space, you name it! A must see!!
